AREN'T good</h2><p id="iyc93j" class="ftparagraph">For a lot of reasons, coaches aren't really GOOD at what they do, which is- the skill of coaching. They don't have a proper roadmap &amp; a community.</p></div><div id="iy8ulb" class="gjs-ft-column gjs-ft-col-md"><div id="ipv05u" class="ft_com_div ft_com_box"><img id="iwz061" sizes="100vw" src="./page_files/a3njk_512_help.png" alt="a3njk_512_help" class="ft_image img-fluid ft_image-style" srcset="https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/320/a3njk_512_help.png 320w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/480/a3njk_512_help.png 480w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/a3njk_512_help.png 768w"></div><h2 id="itut1e" class="ftsub_heading">Complicated Modalities</h2><p id="ik8zca" class="ftparagraph">it takes TOO MUCH time for coaches to get good, because most modalities re complicated, eg- NLP, which takes months/years to even understand.</p></div></div><div id="iiyuue" class="gjs-ft-row"><div id="iq7kjo" class="gjs-ft-column gjs-ft-col-md"><div id="iw8kwk" class="ft_com_div ft_com_box"><img id="ivhqyh" sizes="100vw" src="./page_files/qxmzk_512_communication.png" alt="qxmzk_512_communication" class="ft_image img-fluid ft_image-style" srcset="https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/320/qxmzk_512_communication.png 320w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/480/qxmzk_512_communication.png 480w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/qxmzk_512_communication.png 768w"></div><h2 id="iuemg4" class="ftsub_heading">Ineffective Modalities</h2><p id="irfxof" class="ftparagraph">Other Modalities, Like Affirmations Or General Motivational Sessions Are Simply Ineffective For Coaches As Well As Their Clients. Coaches Don't Know What To Suggest To Their Clients.</p></div><div id="ikvjic" class="gjs-ft-column gjs-ft-col-md"><div id="ig66r8" class="ft_com_div ft_com_box"><img id="ifscdh" sizes="100vw" src="./page_files/czoda_512_stamp.png" alt="czoda_512_stamp" class="ft_image img-fluid ft_image-style" srcset="https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/320/czoda_512_stamp.png 320w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/480/czoda_512_stamp.png 480w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/czoda_512_stamp.png 768w"></div><h2 id="iu881v" class="ftsub_heading">Too Many Certifications</h2><p id="i9j33g" class="ftparagraph">But Not Having Expertise In Any Of Them. Not Taking Enough Action To Help And Giving Results To Clients.</p></div></div><div id="irfov9" class="gjs-ft-row"><div id="id8yys" class="gjs-ft-column gjs-ft-col-md"><div id="idf2lf" class="ft_com_div ft_com_box"><img id="i3epp3" sizes="100vw" src="./page_files/k2ody_512_donate.png" alt="k2ody_512_donate" class="ft_image img-fluid ft_image-style" srcset="https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/320/k2ody_512_donate.png 320w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/480/k2ody_512_donate.png 480w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/k2ody_512_donate.png 768w"></div><h2 id="ibfr28" class="ftsub_heading">Not able to market &amp; monetise</h2><p id="i629ws" class="ftparagraph">most coaches are just one among the big crowd of coaches, without a unique offer, positioning and monetisation strategy.</p></div><div id="ivszbs" class="gjs-ft-column gjs-ft-col-md"><div id="i02x1n" class="ft_com_div ft_com_box"><img id="iqdiw2" sizes="100vw" src="./page_files/gzmzm_512_error.png" alt="gzmzm_512_error" class="ft_image img-fluid ft_image-style" srcset="https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/320/gzmzm_512_error.png 320w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/480/gzmzm_512_error.png 480w,https://img.flexifunnels.com/images/8535/gzmzm_512_error.png 768w"></div><h2 id="icqsr7" class="ftsub_heading">No client results</h2><p id="i3iaqw" class="ftparagraph">and because of all the above factors, coaches don't get success stories, or results</p></div></div><div id="i5ah8n" class="ft_com_div ft_com_box"><a id="ie6c3u" href="https://actionmasterclass.in/checkout-eft" data-popup="flexiPoup_iNwR8f" data-ftbuttontype="website" class="gjs-btn"><span id="ix